name: RBC Target 2031 Canadian Government Bond ETF
longDescription: The fund by investing primarily in a portfolio of fixed-income securities issued by Canadian governments and agencies that mature in the same calendar year as RBC Target 2031 Canadian Government Bond ETFs Termination Date. RBC Target 2031 Canadian Government Bond ETF will terminate on its Termination Date. The investment objective of RBC Target 231 Canadian Government Bond ETF is to provide income, for a limited period of time ending on RBC Target 231 Canadian Government Bond ETFs Termination Date.
